      <dt class="news-tit ellipsis" data-level=""><a target="_blank" href="http://k.sina.com.cn/article_6192937794_17120bb4202000yfvz.html?from=finance">业内人士：公募基金侧袋机制有助应对流动性风险</a></dt>
	  
      
      <dd class="new-info">
      <div class="labels col2"><span class="date">界面</span> | <span class="time">2019年08月19日 07:23</span></div>
      <div class="oper"><a href="http://comment5.news.sina.com.cn/comment/skin/default.html?channel=mp&newsid=6192937794-17120bb4202000yfvz" target="_blank" class="review col2"><i class="CC-icon-review"></i><span class="num" cmnt_id="mp:6192937794-17120bb4202000yfvz:0" name="cmnt_count"></span></a></div>        
